  "title": "fix(chat): update tools api in chat widgets",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\nThis PR updates the tools API in chat widgets to be object-based instead of array-based. Updated usage:\r\n```javascript\r\n<Chat\r\n  tools={{\r\n    alertOnHello: {\r\n      layoutComponent: ({ message, addToolResult }) => {\r\n        return <div/>;\r\n      },\r\n      onToolCall: ({ addToolResult, input, ...toolCallOptions }) => {\r\n        addToolResult({\r\n          output: { text: 'output' },\r\n        });\r\n      },\r\n    },\r\n  }}\r\n/>\r\n```",
